        "outcome": "success",
        "exitCode": 0,
        "reason": "Made fetchDefaultBranchCI accept excludeRunId (auto-detected from GITHUB_RUN_ID) and consult listWorkflowRunsForRepo when the rollup is PENDING with only the self-run in flight, classifying based on the latest completed non-self run. Genuine non-self pending is preserved, no anchor returns unknown, transport errors fall back to the rollup. Cache key now includes excludeRunId so concurrent observers don't pollute each other.",
        "prUrl": "https://github.com/aharonyaircohen/kody-chat/pull/3",
        "runUrl": null,
